LISTSERV Web Interface 2.4.1 2014-07-28T13:57:26Z JiscMail Helpline 2014-07-28T15:57:20+01:00 2014-07-28T15:57:20+01:00 CISCO JiscMail List - is CLOSED https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=CISCO;9f8719d9.1407 We have been unable to find a new list owner therefore JiscMail have CLOSED this list.<br><br>The list is not accepting new subscribers and existing subscribers are no longer able to post messages to the list. The list archives will continue to be available to browse.<br><br>We can reactivate this list if we can find a new list owner. To volunteer please contact us at helpline@jiscmail.ac.uk - we can provide training and support. We have contacted the people who run the list (list owners) to decide on the future of the list, but have not received a response.<br><br>We plan to close and RETAIN the list **w/c 7th July 2014** [...]
